messages.content: Climbing on trees and jumping from them to get around is what Mamizou is doing. This Tanuki doesnt wanna get dirty

Foetidus was picking up berries and other plants for her potions until she heard the sounds of someone jumping from tree to tree.
Instantly, she turned around, looking to see what could be making that noise
There she could see Mamizou jumping while grumbling to herself
She glared at the mun and threw a rock at her, before floating
She yelped and nearly fell "HEY!!! What was that for?!"
She flew up to the mun's level and glared at her, before hitting her with her stick " What are *you* doing in *my* swamp, uh ?"
She yelped again "What makes it your swamp????? And legit I didnt know you owned a whole ass swamp."
she hit her again "I live here, idiot. Now, answer my question, what are *you* doing here"
She hissed at that "I was wandering around trying to figure out how to get my dear Vulpe back."
She sighed "But why *here* exactly ? the void is big, there's many places, and not many wannder here"
"I thought no one lived here. Plus theres alot of trees and not much danger really." She hummed
"Well *I* live here, so now get out if you don't have anything intresting to request"
"Do you know anyway to get someone your destined to be with to come back? She was taken away by that damn Sanguis." She huffed
Foetidus bursted out laughing, holding her stomach "*Oh, my GOD* **'DeStInEd To Be ???'** are you... serious ?? pff, you *really* believe in that stuff ??"
She huffed and looked away "Yeah. I do."
she kept cackling "oh my *god* this is so stupid, are you really that naive ? this is too good" she wiped away her tears of laughter
"Listen can you help me or no? Ill leave if no." She huffed again
She sighed and crossed her arms, looking away "well, I technically *could*" she glanced at her and sligtly grin "If you can pay the price that is"
"Whats the price?"
she crossed her legs and smirk "Depends on what you got, I'm a *witch*, hon, my services are *expenssive*"
"I got munny if thats what you want!"
"... how *much* munny are we talking about here ?"
"Hmmmm...." She said a pretty large amount "I hardly spend it!"
She grinned "You know what ? I'll accept the offer, although it's a little bit on the short side"
Her tail wagged "Yay!"
"*However* you'll have to bring me some hair from the one you want, and maybe some other ingredients too"
"Ok! That shouldn't be too hard to do!" She grinned
"Alright let me just-" she flew back to her shed, and came back with a list, which had 'the lovers' piece of hair' written on it as well as some snacks and plants "Here, the list"
"Alright then Ill get on that~!" She took the list and stood up
"I'll be waiting here, don't forget the munny "
Rosearade is here and just trying to find a cave or a tree to sleep in. Shes very tired...

Foetidus was picking up some ingredients, unitl she heard the sound of *someone* nearby. 
She sighed loudly, a bit frustrated, and started to float towards the noise.
Rosearade eventually just sat on the ground under a tree and tried to get some sleep
Foe finally found the stranger and hit her with her staff "Hey, you, wake up"
She yelped and opened her eyes. "Ah- Sorry....."
she sat in the air, glaring at the mun "what are *you* doing here? this is *my* swamp, so you better get your ass out of here"
"I....didnt know that...Im sorry...Im just...looking for someplace I can rest....Im always kicked out of places...." She stood up "I didnt mean to disturb you.." She rubbed her eyes and yawned
She stared at her for a while "... Don't you have a house or something ? where are your parents even ? "
She shook her head "Dont have any parents......or a house...."

Her expression seemed slightly softer, as she sighed and crossed her arms "So, let me get this straight, you have *no* house, *no* parents, and I'm going to assume you *also* have no family or no job, right ?"

"Yeah....No one wanted me to work for them because I 'will scare away the customers' cause Im a dragon....." She sighed "Pretty sure I have no family....Ive been by myself for as long as I can remember..."
She sighed loudly, rubbing her eyes. She started  floating back to her house, gesturing towards Roserade "Follow me"
She blinked in confusion but followed after her

they ended up in front of a small, rustic house, made out of wood. Foe went back on the ground, and opened the door before giving a key to Roserade "Here, I'll be away for a few days, so I'm giving you my house during that time" 
She walked in, the whole house really only had one big room, a small bed was in a corner. the walls had moss on them, and spider webs all over. On the multiple wooden tables were different jars, bowls, and other things used to hold different materials. 
the thing standing out the most was a mini fridge, powered by a generator
"Oh- uh- t-thank you..." shes still very confused

Foe remained neutral "So, there's no electricity here, aside from the generator you see right there" she was pointing at the mini fridge "Don't touch the generator, you can take the food in the fridge, however."
She then gestured towards the tables "I'd also prefer if you didn't touch *any* of these, understood ?" she turned back to Roserade
She nodded "Alright!" She had a slight wag of her tail

Foe patted her shoulder "Good, if you want to eat something else, you better go buy it, I'll give you some munny" She took some of her stuff, before walking back out 
She then rang a bell that was hanging from a large stick planted in the mud, and a Crocodile came up a few seconds later " This is Kroc, if you have any questions or something you want me to know, write it and give it to him, he'll know where I am. Just ring the bell to call him" She petted the Crocodile
She nodded again and waved ti Kroc
Foe was counting on her hand, mumbling, to see if she forgot anything "Oh, by the way, I hope you don't mind insects crawling on you when you sleep, there's a lot around"
"I don't mind! If I had a cave they would be there too." She hummed
She chuckled " good, glad we're on the same page here." She took her bag and was getting ready to take off before turning around again "Oh, by the way, I'm Foetidus, but just call me Foe"
"Its nice to meet you...Im Rosearade." She smiled a bit
"alright Roserade, I guess I'll see in a few days " she waved, and gave a slight smile, before floating
She waved before going to lay down and actually get some sleep
Foe landed a few miles away, she put her back on the ground and stretched *"Well, time to get to work"*
Rose is a happy dragon
after a few days, Roserade could hear a knock on the door, early in the morning
She woke up and went to go open it, yawning a bit

Foe was standing in front of her, it looked like she hasn't gotten much sleep...
She waved "Morning Rose "
"Hi Foe! You.....look tired..." She was a bit concerned
She brushed it off "come with me, now "
"Alright..." she nodded
She started to float, and was guiding Roserade through a marked path
She followed after her

after a while, they stopped at a house, there was some pieces of wood around still
foe gestured towards it "here, it's your house"
She blinked "R-Really....?" She felt tears welling up and her tail began to wag
she nodded "yeah, I didn't want to have to live with someone else in my house, so I just build one" she was...very tired
"Thank you....Thank you so much Foe!!! You....are the first person to be kind to me...."
she shrugged "eh, it's not much, it's definitly smaller than mine, but I guess it'll do for now"
"Its ok!!!" She was tempted to hug Foe
Foe just did a thumb up, holding on her staff
"Do....you want some help getting back to your house?"
she was silent from a moment, she was very tired but she didn't want to bother Roserade, she just shook her head "nah, I'll be fine"
"You sure??? I dont mind giving you a ride back." She hummed, stretching her wings a bit
she shook her head again "I'll just float, you should go back to sleep, there's a bed in the house"
She nodded a bit "Alright! Let me know if theres anything you need! Ill be glad to get it for you!!"
she nodded before floating off, pretty much falling asleep at this point
She goes into her new home and flops onto the bed
Kroc saw that foe was asleep floating, and chomped on her staff, to guide her back to her house
Rosearade is now up and hungry. She decides perhaps its good to go on a hunt
Stretching a bit the dragon left her home and flew up into the air
Her hunt was going well. That was until, she got a little too cocky. She ended up flying right into a tree, a sickening _CRACK_ could be heard from one of her wings
Rosearade screamed out in pain as she fell out of said tree. "F-fuck- my wing...." She gently touched it, yelping from the pain.
She sniffled a bit and flys up into the air, trying to ignore the pain.
She gets home and falls to the ground. Her wings hurts so much....
She gets into her house and lays on her bed in pain.
She has no way of wrapping it or making a splint. She needs help. She hates to do this hut shes gonna have to ask Foe for help...
She gets up, her broken wing still open, her other folded up. Off she goes to Foes!
Eventually she gets there and knocks on the door, trying to not cry from the pain
Foe rolled in her bed, and begrudgingly float to the door, opening it eyes half closed "mm what"
"H-Hi....So-sorry to bother you b-but....I....I broke my wing....an-and I....need help.....fixing it....." One of her wings was simply hanging down. She couldn't fold it due to the pain

Foe blinked, slowly, trying to process what's going on "... Ah" she gently made Rose float in the air, her wing felt very light. 
she started to look into her stuff
She played with her hands nervously

Foe found some bandages she had, as well as an old potion that she gave to rose "drink this" 
She started to patch up Roserade's wing
She nodded and drank it "Th-Thank you...."
she sighed "be more careful, the swamps are big, you could easly get lost"
She nodded, wiping her eyes a bit
"looks like you'll have to stay on the ground for a week at least" she touched roserade and she fell on the ground gently
She nodded "Alright...." This is gonna be hell
Shes vibing her house, trying to deal with her wing
Buneries is here, their tail swishing nervously as they try and find Foe. They knew she delt with potions and stuff so maybe she could help
Foe couldn't sleep, and was looking for some ingredients again, she was tired and didn't noticed Bunaries at first.
Buneries saw her and walked over "You're Foetidus yeah??? I need your help...." They gently tapped her shoulder
Foe instantly turned around, took a step back and hit buneries with her stick "Who are you ?"
She yelped a bit "My name is Buneries. Listen can you make an antidote to poison??? A mun I know, Sarcio, fought Morise and got poisoned. I have no idea how long he has to live....."
Foe hissed "You're a plasma, aren't you ? get out of my swamp, I am *not* helping your kind"
"Does that really matter?! A mun is _dying_ because Morise _poisoned_ him. I need your help! I dont want him to die!"
She shook her head, rubbing her eyes "wow wow *wow* why would *you* care about a mun? Aren't you plasma... *supposed* to be on the same side and all?"

"Im not on the side of the Plasma. Im on the side on the muns. I hate what the others have done. Ive always tried to stop them but no matter what I did they ignored it." They sighed "So just, i dont care if you hate me but _please_ help Sarcio."
She sighed and calmed down "Fine. but this better not be some kind of dirty trick, alright ? I will *try* but I won't promise anything"
They nodded "Thank you...."
She started to float "Do you have an extract of the poison, or *anything* that could help indentifying it ?"
"I know its from a scorpion tail.....if that helps..."
"Uh" she took a minute to think "I mean, depends on *what* scorpion... Poisons are complex, and making a "work on everyting" kind of antidote is impossible"
"I.....Have no idea..." They frowned a bit, starting to oace around
She was laying in the hair for a bit, thinking, before getting back to Buneries " Is there anyway I could see this mun ? I could try to figure out what *kind* it is "
They nod "Yeah hes at his house. Ive been caring for him...."
"Alright, I'll take some of my stuff, and you'll guide me to his house" She floated back to her house, gestering towards them, so they follow her
They follow after her, tail swishing nervously still
Once they arrived at her house, she told them to wait outside, and a few minutes after, she came back with a bag, full of different stuff she packed quickly "Alright, let's go"
They nod and begin to walkt o Saricos house
She followed, floating
To #sarcios-house
Mamizou is here, looking for Foe
Foe noticed her, as she was coming back to her house "Oh, *you*"
"Hi! Got the stuff you asked for~" She smiled
"Oh, nice" She signed to her "I'm heading to my house, follow me"
She nodded and followed after her
After some time, they arrived to her house. Foe dropped her stuff on the ground and landed "Alright, just put it somewhere, I'll get to it in a sec"
She nodded and put it on a nearby table
Foe got her stuff ready to brew, and pushed Mamizou out "Alright, stay here, I'll have them done in no time"
She nodded and waited

Foe was picking the ingredients left and right with her hair, smirking to herself *ohohoh. perfect* 
She was brewing two potion, one was an actual Love potion, but would only last half an hour, while the other was actually a 'reverse' potion, and would make everyone who drank it act and say the opposite of what they wanted. She would make Mamizou drink the reverse potion, making her think it's necessary for the love potion to work *genius*
However, during the making of the love potion, a part of her more... *fleshy* pot fell in it. Oh well, *surely* it'll be fine.
Mamizou was excited. Finally! Vulpe would realize that she was the only mun she loved and not her silly boyfriend! She would finally have Vulpe all to herself.

After a bit, Foe finally got out, two potions in hand, one was blue, ans labeled '4 Mamizou' and the second was pink and labeled '4 Vulpe' 
"Alright, here."
"Oh! Theres one I have to drink as well?" She tilted her head a bit
"Yeah, otherwise the love potion won't work, I mean, if she drank it alone, she would fall in love with *anyone* you know" she calmly explained, hiding her smirk perfectly
She nodded a bit "Ohhh I see! Interesting! Well thank you~!"
"No problem, as long as I'm paid, I don't mind " she chuckled
She nodded and gave her the payment, tail wagging a bit
She happily took the munny, counting and humming "Alright, it's all here, thanks !"
"No problem and thank you again~!" She giggled before excitedly running off
She waved, and once she was out of sight, she began laughing her ass off

The foliage crunched under Sanguis’s feet as he entered the swamp, geez, what a fixer upper.....nevermind, he wouldn’t be here for much long....
Foe instantly heard him, and floated up to the noises, her stick in hand
Not hearing her, he continued his escapade, looking around the area for a house, abnormally large tree, anything that can signify someone living there. He’s starting to get agitated
Foe decided hit him from behind with her staff, still in the air "Get out of my swamp"

The mun whipped around, practically fuming, and swatted the stick away, “**Don’t. Fucking. Hit. Me**.” He growled, He wanted to hit-no *break* something but for the sake of not pissing off the wrong person right now.....he’s just....bottling it up “..... you’re Foe then?”
Foe glared at him, surprised "Yes, I am, what do you *want*"
“What I **want** would be information regarding a certain love potion.” He glared right back, crossing his arms,
Foe stayed silent for a bit, before letting out a loud laugh "Oh, *the raccoon*'s potion ? Ah, you must be the one she wanted to take her love from, don't worry, it'll be fine"
The laughing caused his eyes to twitched, *did she think this is a fucking joke?!*.  “I don’t think it’ll be ‘*fine*’.” He said through gritted teeth.
"trust me, I'm not *stupid* enough to give dirty raccoons like her what they want" she gently put her staff on sanguis head "just come back to her in half an hour, and you'll see"
All that anguish, all that frustration, that was bottled, dissolved with an exasperated sigh... “Really?....I....oh god was that really it?.....maybe I went too hard on that Tanuki....” he facepalmed
"The love potion only last 30 minutes" She smirked "And that girl was stupid enough to drink another potion I gave her, making her act and say the reverse of what she wants" She laughed
“O-Oh.....I just....Sorry I...need a moment...” he slumps down by a tree, rubbing his temples.
"The *best* part is that she paid an *absurd* amount of munny for it, I'm rich !" she chuckled and sighed "I can't wait to see her face when she'll realised what happened"

“If she’s still alive.....Vulpes gonna go feralllineedtogo.” His eyes widen as a thought hit him, *whats she gonna be like after the potion??*. As much of a pain in the ass Mamazou is.....no one really deserves that fate...
Foe shrugged "eh, not my problem. She probably deserve it"
Rose is here! Shes tired but happy in her new clothing...
Foe was outside and rushed up to her, thinking it was a stranger at first  "Oh, Rose, it's you, I see you got some new clothes"
"Hey Foe! Yeah I went shopping with a mun named Quartz! It was...alot of fun." She smiled, tail wagging a bit
"Good, good! Glad to see you're making friends" she looked at her wings, suspicious "What's up with your wings ?"
"Ah- I.....Ended up...making the injury worse during the whole world tilting thing ..." She rubbed her arm nervously
"World tilting ? " she tilted her head. looks like she *barely* noticed it
"You....didnt notice??? Something cause the world to tilt.....Lots of Muns got hurt..."
"ah" she sighed " I was floating, I guess I was too lost in my own head"
"Ah...Well...Im glad youre safe..."
she chuckled "it's gonna take more than *that* to get rid of this old witch !"
Her tail wagged and she chuckled
"I can get ya a healing potion, I should have enough for it " she started to float " won't cure it instantly, but it'll help"
She nodded "That sounds like a good idea....Thanks Foe."
"no problem" she was floating back home "I'm not gonna let you with a broken wing"
She followed after her "Ill be ok eventually..."
"better sooner than later, right ?" she shrugged, and they arrived to her house "I'll go brew it"
She nodded and waited
after a while, she got out with a potion "here, drink it. It's bitter as all hell"
She nodded and drank it begore sticking her tounge out "Bleh."
she smirked "told ya" she opened her door "want something to eat?"
She nodded "Yeah!!"
Foe walked in, and pointed to a small chair "sit here " she looked through her mini fridge "anything you'd like in particular ?"
She sat down "Uhhh nope! Not really "
"alright" she pulled out a bag of chips and some cookies "want a drink ?"
"Water please!!!"
she threw at Rose a bottle of fresh water and put the food on the table "it's not much, but it's a nice snack"
"Thank you Foe!" She began to eat her snacks
"no problem" she made herself some tea and was floating in a sitting position "so, how was your day?"
"Pretty good!!!! I had alot of fun shopping!!!!!! I also helped Quartz  cut her hair!!!" She smiled "I also met Opal, Vega, and Akousa!"
"uh, that's a lot of people" she took a sip of her tea "they weren't scared of you ?"
She kinda froze up "No....but....someone at the pizza place was ....Quartz....stood up for me...." She looked away
"uh, she did ?" she took another sip "good. I like this quartz"
Her tail wagged a bit at that "oh!! Thats good to know..."
"She sounds like she doesn't take shit from anyone, a very good quality"
"She really doesnt!"
"Good for her !" she chuckled
".....Have....you ever been in love....?" She asked
She took one, *very* long sip "As far as I know, I haven't. Might've been in my human life, but I can't remember... why ?"
"....I think im in love. With Quartz......"
she spit out her tea "You ***what***"
She played with her hands "I-Im not so sure yet. Ive never been in love before....But i feel....really happy around her...."
"you.... you barely know her? " she shook her head "Look, I don't know shit about love, I fear I can't be much help"
"I know...." She sighed
She shrugged "I guess you'll just wait and see"
She nodded "Shes pretty cool...Her family is nice too..."
"uh, must be nice, to have a cool family " she muttered taking another sip
"I think your cool!" She hummed
she chuckled " I wouldn't say I'm the defintion of cool, but thanks"
"Youre welcome." She grinned
"Meanwhile, I was tricking a raccoon lookin' mun " she cackled "*god* she was stupid"
"Oh?? Tell me more..." She was interested

She snickered "Oh my god she sounds so stupid."

"You tricked her well!!" She giggled

she shrugged "Guess we'll wait"

"Come on outside. Ill show you." She grinned
she made her cup of tea kinda just... float in midair and went outside
She went outside and shifted into her dragon form
"HOLY ***SHIT***" she put her hands on her head, confused yet impress
"Neat huh?" She lowered her head to meet hers
"'Neat'???? it's fucking ***fantastic***" she still was hardly believing it
She grinned "Thanks~!"
"I didn't know muns could just... do that? or at least some"

she nodded "Yeah! helps with potions a lot"
She yawned a bit then

She nodded

"It's nothin'" she started to walk to Rose's house

*Why, exactly, do I not like mud?* Venor wonders to herself as she trudges around in circles. *I have dealt with it for so long, in so many timelines. But.* She wrinkles her nose and steps in a puddle. *It's gross.* She continues on, as quietly as she can go. She's testing out her quietness in unfamiliar terrain.
Foetidus was collecting some plants, her hearing was *very* sharp, especially in the swamps she knew so well *someone's around. has been a while* She started to float towards the sounds of Venor.

Venor freezes, sending out a scan of emotional closeness to try see who's around. A radar based on emotions. Interesting. Sensing Foetidus vaguely, she whips out her bow and drops into a crouch, nocking an arrow.

Foe was a few meters up the ground, looking around the area. After a while, she spotted Venor and noticed her bow *urg. why does this one has a weapon*. She decided to approach her in a more friendly manner than usual, and yelled from above **"Hey, The hell you're doing here?"**
((mORE FRIENDLY-))
((*USUALLY IT'S THE BONK WITH THE STICK ALRIGHT*

Venor yelps and releases the arrow with pinpoint accuracy. "Who the hell are *you*?" She yells upwards. She takes a few more arrows from her quiver and summons her stand, opening eyes on top of her head to see better.

Foe attempted to dodge the arrow, but she wasn't fast enough and it managed to hit her right in the shoulder, she hissed *"JESUS CHRIST YOU MOTHERFUCK-"* . She applied a slight pressure to her new wound, as a reflex "I'm the one who lives here, *dipshit*!" She yelled back, summoning her own stand.

"You *yelled* at me!" Venor yells, rolling her top pair of eyes. "Now come down here so we can discuss things *civilly*." Careless Whisper wraps itself around her, draping its head across her shoulders.

"You fucking *shoot* me!" she yelled back, slowly going down, the arrow still stuck in her shoulder. Magnets stared at Venor, *clearly* not amused, and stayed behind Foe. She was still floating in the air, sitting.
"You *yelled* at me, a person that has a *criminal* for a human?? Obviously there's people like me who respond with violence." Venor opens some eyes on the back of her hands, glaring.
Rose had been sleeping until she heard the commotion. She flew over and landed nearby "Whats going on here??" She asked, wings spread out for intimidation factor
Venor yelps and nocks another arrow.
Foe, as fast as possible, jumped in the way of the arrow, managing to stop it with her hand. She had an arrow stabbing her hand now. "What the *fuck* ????" she hissed towards Venor
"Jesus *christ*. Are you going to kill me or something?" Venor slowly raises her bow. "Don't do anything without warning around me, I *swear to god.*"
"Oh, I don't *know* could you chill for like *five minutes* and *not* attack someone like that???" She gestured to Rose with her hand, clearly *pissed* at Venor
"You snuck up on me without any warning, and then someone comes to support you?? I'm outnumbered, I'm basically raising my weapon away from me-" Venor splutters.
Rose shifts into her dragon form, getting protective over Foe "Leave her alone." She snarled "She acts this way to everyone who enters the swamp. This is her home after all."

"Yeah, when someone breaks into my home, I don't yell at them. I wasn't even doing anything, I was practicing walking on new terrain!" Venor glares and Careless Whisper floats up to sit on her shoulder.
"I literally just asked you *why* you were here, the fucking arrow was *uncalled for*" She was getting frustrated "*sorry* for being protective of my *own damn property*"
"Okay, you nock an arrow and try not to release it when you get startled." She retorts. "And I honestly didn't know. Jesus."
She groaned "Fine *fine*" She turned to Rose "Would you mind giving us a flight to my house? I uh, kinda of have stuff to treat" she vaguely gestured to her wounded shoulder with her wounded hand
"You're just going to go... Who even are you?" Venor folds her arms. "People *say* I should be more socially orientated but how the hell is that gonna happen when this... You know what, nevermind."
Rose nodded "Yeah bo probably. Im Rosearade by the way. As you can tell, im a dragon."
"The name's foetidus, but just call me Foe" she floated to Rose and jumped on her back "If you wanna be more social, I have tea, so come if that what you want" she shrugged
"Uhh. Sure." So *this* is how you make friends.
((ah yes, the old arrow in the shoulder. flawless friendship technique
"Here. Get on my back." She hummed, lowering a wing for her "Ill fly us there"
"O...kay." Venor cautiously steps on.
"Alright Rose, let's go. you better be careful....*whatever your name is*"
"Venor." *Or Two.* She swallows. "I'm always careful."
She spreads her wings and takes off
"alright, venor. I'd say 'nice to meet you' but I'm still bitter about the *arrows*"
"I'm still bitter about the yelling." Venor says flatly.
"At least you aren't *wounded*" She replied, sharply
"And how do you know that? Words can *hurt*, my dear Foe." Venor reels dramatically.
"didn't seem to affect you that much, *dearVenor*" she responded smugly
"Of course not. I don't have that level of emotion yet." Venor raises her eyebrows and her stand facepalms in the distance.
"Oi. Cut it out." Rose hissed as she landed at Foes house
"Wait. *What do you mean you don't have that level of emotion yet*" She looked ar Venor, confused, as she jumped off Rose

Venor hums and does a casual leap off. "Counting by the colours in my mindscape, I have four emotions in total. Maybe five, but that's specific to Venandi, I think." She muses to herself. "Until recently, I didn't have emotions." She says casually.

"H...W... *How*" She was struggling to even *think* of what to say. She brushed it off "We'll talk about it after I'm done with my ***wounds***" She glanced at Venor "Rose, help me with them" She entered her house
Rose shifted into mun form "On it!!"
"Oh. Yeah, I keep a healing kit for my arrows if I stab anyone with them accidentally. If you need them." Venor says, still very casually.

"I got my own stuff, I'll be *fine*" She proceed to sit in the air "Alrightn Rose, I want you to take this arrows out, and put the cloth right here on it *as fast as possible*" she pointed to a pile of cloth nearby
